Write a function in C++ to find the median of an unsorted array.

### Response:
int findMedian(int arr[], int n)
{
    sort(arr, arr+n);
    if (n % 2 != 0)
       return arr[n/2];

    return (arr[(n-1)/2] + arr[n/2])/2;
}

